# raw per-turn protocol dumps from analysis/run_ablation.py and trace_matchup.py -
# huge (tens of thousands of lines per config) and mostly useful for one-off deep dives,
# unlike decisions.csv/per_bot*.csv/summary.csv which stay small and are what the report
# actually cites, so those remain tracked.
analysis/results/**/events.csv

# ignore everything inside players/
showdown_agent/scripts/players/*

# but do not ignore the players directory itself nor rename.py
!showdown_agent/scripts/players/
!showdown_agent/scripts/players/rename.py